        },
        "actions": {
          "value": null
        },
        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>One of Mithrodar's four anchors</strong> — and a <em>living</em> one: he gets a few miles' hunting radius, no more. Mithrodar's compulsion (@Check[type:perception|dc:28] after a minute's conversation to sense it) forbids him to explain the anchor mechanism or openly ally. Slaying him — or disrupting Mithrodar's control (antimagic and the like) — advances the curse-breaking by one stage.</p>"
        },
